recent projects				<h3>Our Latest Case Studies 				</h3>Works 				
		<p style="text-align: center;">All functions including supply chain, value chain, project scheduling, manufacturing, services and spares, technology, R&amp;D, etc. are integrated to give a complete solutions package.</p>		
